# Example env for Trip Planner
# Set the Groq chat model to use at build/runtime. If omitted, code falls back to llama-3.1-8b-instant.
VITE_GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.1-8b-instant

# In production, prefer a server-side proxy and keep the API key server-side.
# e.g. GROQ_API_KEY (used by your serverless function)
